{"tid":2393964,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國警察以刑毀罪拘捕攝影師 因拍攝難民示威照片及放到Twitter上","createTime":"2021-02-04T01:07:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-04T02:56:56.000Z","uid":10540,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7514fffede7de76fdefe23588651f7055d752701","tid":2393964,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T01:07:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://photoblog.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/aa_01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2Faa_01.jpg&h=42bbf703&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n於 1 月 28 日當日，有示威者去到軍營前示威，要求內政部關閉設施。示威者將假血撥向入口處，並高舉標語「Close Napier camp or​ ​there will be blood on your hands (關閉納皮爾否則你會滿手鮮血」，指當局處理不當會引發更多激烈衝突。示威當日在場拍攝採訪的 Andy Aitchison，拍攝了數張相片並放在 Twitter 上公開，亦被多家媒採用。數小時後，5 名警員登門將其拘捕，控告 Andy Aitchison 當日涉嫌刑事毁壞，並扣留他的手提電話及記憶卡，至當晚上10時才容許保釋外出直至 2 月 22 日為止，期間不可再接近納皮爾軍營。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://photoblog.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/aa_7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2Faa_7.jpg&h=dd9794bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n英國當地的國家記者聯盟 (The Nation Union of Journalists) 對 Aitchison 被捕亦表達極度關注。聯盟組織者 Pamela Morten 指出 Aitchison當日僅負責紀錄現場，並沒有參與任何示威。她指出新聞收集者的主要工作就是基於公眾利益對事件作出報導，警方不應該作出任何干預、防範或限制記者紀錄事件的行為。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://photoblog.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/aa_8-732x800.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2Faa_8-732x800.jpg&h=caacdcae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而在獨立報的報導中，Aitchison 這樣形容他的處境：「這看起來像政治事件，有人指出了那裏情況有多壞，而我就將訊息分享出去，亦因此我被針對了。這會影響我的餘生及工作。」<br />\n<br />\n內政部發言人未就拘捕事件作出評論，僅指出破壞公物不可接受，以及違反隔離令會被罰款。而在健康保護條例下，以記者或攝影師身份工作而離開住所，僅被視為「合理」藉口。而有關難民對他們自身健康及安全的擔憂，內政部則認為評價該處對難民不夠妥善實屬冒犯，態度強硬。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://photoblog.hk/279044/%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E6%94%9D%E5%BD%B1-andy-aitchison-%E6%8B%8D%E6%94%9D%E9%9B%A3%E6%B0%91%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E7%AB%9F%E8%A2%AB%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E6%8B%98%E6%8D%95%E5%8F%8A%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%91\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2F279044%2F%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2594%259D%25E5%25BD%25B1-andy-aitchison-%25E6%258B%258D%25E6%2594%259D%25E9%259B%25A3%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E7%25AB%259F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%258B%2598%25E6%258D%2595%25E5%258F%258A%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E5%2588%2591&d=f02Xtm2mX5FaAGCExHUdjTvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=5e3e3094\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://photoblog.hk/279044/%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E6%94%9D%E5%BD%B1-andy-aitchison-%E6%8B%8D%E6%94%9D%E9%9B%A3%E6%B0%91%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E7%AB%9F%E8%A2%AB%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E6%8B%98%E6%8D%95%E5%8F%8A%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%91</a>"},{"pid":"448e6b3d9c626ce5af49cb99590f5a18f186e3b1","tid":2393964,"uid":259901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T01:14:35.000Z","msg":"天下黑警一樣黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce9b01fcde6f5d0a223e4af415e0fc8305ec235d","tid":2393964,"uid":282569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T01:21:56.000Z","msg":"ACAB"},{"pid":"5e4b8b374b64c1ccb92b13465d4e68cac2125a5a","tid":2393964,"uid":78016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T01:24:27.000Z","msg":"究竟仲有邊個國家係少左膠<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"696b443e7c376aff11d07b601f3c18393a553435","tid":2393964,"uid":266503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e4b8b374b64c1ccb92b13465d4e68cac2125a5a","tid":2393964,"uid":78016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T01:24:27.000Z","msg":"究竟仲有邊個國家係少左膠<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T01:36:50.000Z","msg":"歐洲係左膠大本營"},{"pid":"9ae62cfa626f3c093f40557fe2f3027d1992fce9","tid":2393964,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T01:41:47.000Z","msg":"應該告唔入, 只係想用法庭禁足令阻止你再去現場 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9cb2224d76d3746a630b92ce541c3027c1a090d","tid":2393964,"uid":34869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"696b443e7c376aff11d07b601f3c18393a553435","tid":2393964,"uid":266503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e4b8b374b64c1ccb92b13465d4e68cac2125a5a","tid":2393964,"uid":78016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T01:24:27.000Z","msg":"究竟仲有邊個國家係少左膠<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T01:36:50.000Z","msg":"歐洲係左膠大本營"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T01:44:51.000Z","msg":"班左膠只會搞自己國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24087c56832e0c539d89e7c2c1a15399d898f381","tid":2393964,"uid":144541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T02:56:56.000Z","msg":"核彈"}]}